Titolo: Okage: Shadow King

Anno: 2001

Descrizione: Okage: Shadow King, known in Japan as Boku to Maō (ボクと魔王, Boku to Maō, literally "Me and the Devil King"), is a role-playing video game developed by Zener Works and co-developed and published by Sony Computer Entertainment. It was released on March 15, 2001 in Japan, and October 1, 2001 in North America, exclusively for the PlayStation 2. The game was made available on the PlayStation 4 in March 2016 through the PlayStation Network, as well as being released in Europe for the first time.